NG0506:2722: zhal ni thal le bzhugs pa yin //
NG0506:2723: chos nyid rol pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NG0506:2725: dbus su lha tshogs rang gi lha //
NG0506:2726: gang mos rig pa'i sgyu 'phrul yin //
NG0506:2727: sgyu 'phrul dra ba mngon rdzogs pas //
NG0506:2728: byang chub ci nas bdag thob 'gyur //
NG0506:2729: gzhal yas khang la phyi nang med //
NG0506:2730: phyogs ris med pas kun gyi zhing *//
NG0506:2731: rdul gcig steng na mkha' dang mnyam //
NG0506:2732: rgyal ba rgya mtsho ma lus kyang *//
NG0506:2733: zhi khro'i lha ru 'dus pa yin //
NG0506:2734: de yang rgyal ba rigs lngar 'dus //
NG0506:2735: rigs lngar ma 'dus lha gzhan med //
NG0506:2736: lus sems khyab tshad thams cad la //
NG0506:2737: phung po lnga ni rigs lnga yab /
NG0506:2738: khams lnga yum lnga nyid du gnad //
NG0506:2739: rang byung rang las bskyed pa yi //
NG0506:2741: 'bru lnga ye shes sa bon las //
NG0506:2742: dbus su rnam snang kun tu zhal //
NG0506:2743: gti mug dag pa chos kyi dbyings //
NG0506:2744: longs spyod ye shes 'khor lo rnams //
NG0506:2745: mnyam yang zhabs gnyis skyil krung bzhugs //
NG0506:2746: de las shar phyogs mi bskyod pa //
NG0506:2747: 'od ldan zhe sdang rnam dag pa'i //
NG0506:2748: me long ye shes rdo rje rnams //
NG0506:2749: rin chen gser 'od lho phyogs su //
NG0506:2750: nga rgyal rnam dag mnyam pa nyid //
NG0506:2751: longs spyod rtags su rin chen 'dzin //
NG0506:2752: nub phyogs mtha' yas dmar ba'i 'od //
NG0506:2753: 'dod chags rang grol so sor rtogs //
NG0506:2754: bde stong ye shes pad+ma rnams //
NG0506:2755: byang du don grub mar gad mdog / phrag dog dag pa bya grub 'od //
NG0506:2756: ye shes ldan pa'i rgya gram rnams //
NG0506:2757: mtshan bzang 'od kyis spras pa yi //
NG0506:2758: nyi ma 'char ka'i dkyil ltar mdzes //
NG0506:2759: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa'i //
NG0506:2763: gsang yum 'od kyi rig ma ni //
NG0506:2766: dbyings phyug gsang ba'i yum lnga ni //
NG0506:2768: sku gsung thugs yon 'phrin las lnga'o //
NG0506:2769: 'od kyi rang sprul rigs kyi lha //
NG0506:2770: dpag med mtha' yas mngon zhen bskyed //
NG0506:2771: rdo rje mthong thos myong reg dang *//
NG0506:2772: mthong byed thos byed myong byed dang *//
NG0506:2773: reg byed thabs kyi sems dpa' brgyad //
NG0506:2774: de bzhin pad+ma mthong ba ma //
NG0506:2775: mthong byed la sogs sems ma brgyad //
NG0506:2776: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs rnams dang *//
NG0506:2777: gnyis su med pa'i dkyil 'khor dang *//
NG0506:2778: la se ma le 'gar ti hri //
NG0506:2779: phyag rgya mchod yon lnga sogs kyi //
NG0506:2780: rang las rang 'byung mchod pa'i lha //
NG0506:2781: 'dzin pa chen po lcags kyu zhags //
NG0506:2782: rdo rje lcags sgrog dril bu che //
NG0506:2783: phyi nang kun tu 'joms byed pa'i //
NG0506:2784: sna tshogs rin chen 'phreng ba'i lha //
NG0506:2785: gsal 'tsher lhun sdug gzi brjid ldan //
NG0506:2788: mtha' yas mu med brjod mi lang *//
NG0506:2789: zhing gi rdul snyed gsal bar 'gyur //
NG0506:2790: zhi ba'i ngang las ma g.yos par //
NG0506:2791: thabs kyis gdug pa 'dul ba'i phyir //
NG0506:2792: sems can lus kyi rtsa nang na /
NG0506:2793: khro tshogs rig pa'i lha dgu gnas //
NG0506:2794: drag po'i mngon par spyod 'khor bsgrol //
NG0506:2795: mya ngan 'das pa'i don la sbyor //
NG0506:2797: dur khrod 'bar ba'i gzhal yas su //
NG0506:2798: dregs pa 'joms byed gdan stengs su //
NG0506:2799: sku gsum ldan phyir zhal gsum pa //
NG0506:2800: dkar dmar sku mdog mthing nag dbus //
NG0506:2801: shin tu rngam pa'i gdengs zhal can //
NG0506:2802: ban d+hu dmar po'i spyan dang ldan //
NG0506:2803: phyag drug pha rol phyin drug ldan //
NG0506:2804: rdo rje gri gug 'khor lo g.yas //
NG0506:2805: dril bu ban d+ha bum pa mchog / g.yon pa'i phyag na bsnams pa yis //
NG0506:2806: zhabs gnyis rtag chad bdud bzhi rdzi //
NG0506:2807: dur khrod 'bar ba'i rgyan gyis brgyan //
NG0506:2808: 'ag+hu ya gsang ba dbyings phyug sbyor //
NG0506:2809: mthing nag gri khug thod khrag 'dzin //
NG0506:2810: dpal chen sku la rdzogs pa'i lha //
NG0506:2811: spyi bor ya man ta ka'i sku //
NG0506:2813: thugs khar rdo rje ki la ya //
NG0506:2814: phyogs bcu'i bgegs rnams 'joms byed pa //
NG0506:2815: rnam rgyal hum dkar stobs po che //
NG0506:2816: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba dbyug sngon can //
NG0506:2817: 'dod pa'i rgyal dang trai log kya //
NG0506:2818: dbyings phyug drags byed khro mo'i tshogs //
NG0506:2819: so so'i gnas dang dgyes par 'khril //
NG0506:2821: 'phra men ma tshogs drag po dang *//
NG0506:2822: mkha' 'gro ma mo'i tshogs rnams kun //
NG0506:2823: lhag pa'i ye shes rol pa yin //
NG0506:2825: nam mkha'i lus can thogs med pa'i //
NG0506:2826: stong gsal rig pa'i ye shes lnga //
NG0506:2827: rnam shes tshogs brgyad rdo rje sems //
NG0506:2830: thabs dang shes rab bdag nyid kyi //
NG0506:2831: gnyis su med pa'i rgyud rnams las //
NG0506:2832: dkyil 'khor ming ni gtso bo ste //
NG0506:2833: gtso bo dpal chen he ru ka / he ni rgyu sogs stong pa ste //
NG0506:2834: ru ni tshogs dang bral ba las //
NG0506:2835: ka ni gang du mi gnas pa'i //
NG0506:2836: sgra gsum bdag nyid chen po de //
NG0506:2837: mngon par rtogs pa gsal gyur na /
NG0506:2839: dkyil 'khor bdag po gtso bo yin //
NG0506:2840: gtso bor rdo rje 'dzin pa mchod //
NG0506:2841: mnyam nyid mi g.yo'i ngang las su //
NG0506:2842: rang shar 'od kyi lha tshogs la //
NG0506:2843: don la gtso 'khor khyad med de //
NG0506:2844: thun mong spyi yi gtso bo ste //
NG0506:2845: bye brag dgos su gtso bo yin //
NG0506:2846: rang nyid yid la gang byed pa //
NG0506:2847: de nyid lha yi gtso bo yin //
NG0506:2849: 'khor lo sgyur ba stobs po che //
NG0506:2851: sna tshogs tshul ldan don cig 'grub //
NG0506:2852: gdod nas lhun grub byang chub sems //
NG0506:2853: 'gro kun ma rig rtogs bya'i phyir //
NG0506:2854: snang ba spyi yul sprul pa'i sku //
NG0506:2855: shaka thub rgyal sras 'phags pa'i tshogs //
NG0506:2857: gang gis de nyid don mthong bas //
NG0506:2858: nang gi 'dzin sems mi dmigs pa //
NG0506:2859: kun bzang bde gshegs rigs lnga'i bdag / thams cad mkhyen pa chos kyi sku //
NG0506:2860: kun brtags gzhan rkyen ma yin pa //
NG0506:2861: rang la yod phyir rtog par bya //
NG0506:2862: om mu ne mu ne ma ha mu ne //
NG0506:2863: bo de swa ta sarba sid swa rba hum /
NG0506:2864: d+harma ka ya sarba sid d+hi swa rba hum //
NG0506:2865: thams cad rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor la //
NG0506:2866: rang 'byung ye shes rang grol su //
NG0506:2867: rgyal sras 'phags pa'i tshogs rnams la //
NG0506:2869: rang grol bzhin du gzhan la bstan //
NG0506:2871: gdul ka 'dul ba rnams kyi mchog / 'jam dpal dpa' bos mkhyen pa //
NG0506:2873: ma bcos lus kyi dkyil 'khor na //
NG0506:2874: gsang ba 'dus pa'i lha ru bzhugs //
NG0506:2875: om ba gi shwa ri mum /
NG0506:2879: pradz+nya dz+nya na mur ta ye /
NG0506:2880: dz+nya na ka ya ba gi shwa ra /
NG0506:2882: ya te na ma swa ha //
NG0506:2883: om badzra g+h+rig g+hu h+ya dz+nya na swarba sid d+hi hum hum hum //
NG0506:2884: 'jam dpal mchog la brten nas su //
NG0506:2885: shes rab spobs pa bskyed par bya //
NG0506:2886: thugs rje chen po spyan ras gzigs //
NG0506:2888: bde ba mchog gi rang bzhin can //
NG0506:2889: sgrub par 'dod na tshul bzhin rtogs //
NG0506:2892: om shri badzra he he ru ru kam hum phat /
NG0506:2893: da ki ni dza la sam b+ha ra hum hum /
NG0506:2894: om hri ha ha hum hum phat /
NG0506:2895: thugs rje'i 'phrin las rnam gsum gyis //
NG0506:2896: 'jig rten thams cad sgrol bar byed //
NG0506:2897: thun mong mchog thob bde chen 'gro //
NG0506:2898: phyag na rdo rje'i nus pa yis //
NG0506:2899: phyi rol bar chad zlog par byed //
NG0506:2900: dgyes pa rdo rjes dngos grub thob //
NG0506:2902: ye shes he ru ka / bdag med chos dang yang dag sbyor //
NG0506:2903: phyi nang thabs kyi khyad par yin //
NG0506:2904: om badzra pa ni hum phat /
NG0506:2905: om badzra ni lam b+ha ra d+ha ra d+ha ra hri ta ya hum phat /
NG0506:2906: om badzra tsan d+ha rong na ni hum phat //
NG0506:2907: om badzra ka ru na ca la le hum phat //
NG0506:2908: om d+he bi tsu badzra hum hum phat phat /
NG0506:2909: om badzra ka d+ha ri he badzra hum phat /
NG0506:2918: gang gis sgrub pa'i thabs brtsams pa //
NG0506:2919: gtor mas las kun grub par byed //
NG0506:2920: phyi nang chags med gtor ma ste //
NG0506:2921: ji ltar rigs par bsgrub pos btang *//
NG0506:2922: nad dang nyon mongs 'dul ba'i phyir //
NG0506:2923: khrog dang phye ma'i sbyor ba la //
NG0506:2924: yon tan bdud rtsi phyi nang gnyis //
NG0506:2925: zhi dang khro bor bstan pa'o //
NG0506:2926: om ma ha sarba pan tsa a mri ta badzra tsit+ta sa ma ya hum hum hum /
NG0506:2927: om sarba pan tsa a mri ta ra sa ya na badzra g+hu ya sid ti hum hum /
NG0506:2928: om ru lu ru lu hum b+h+yo hum /
NG0506:2929: man 'dzu shri ya man ta ka hum /
NG0506:2930: pad+ma ta krid ha ya 'ag+h+ri ba hu lu hu lu hum /
NG0506:2931: badzra ki li ki la sarba big nan bam hum phat /
NG0506:2932: sarba pan tsa a mri ta kun da li hum hri tha //
NG0506:2933: skye bdun ril bu'i 'phrin las kyis //
NG0506:2934: sman mchog ye shes yon tan gyis //
NG0506:2936: rigs lnga chen mo gzungs kyi lha //
NG0506:2937: las kyi lha mo sgrol mo ni //
NG0506:2938: rnal 'byor ma yi gzugs kyis su //
NG0506:2939: sngags rnams kun gyi don grub pa //
NG0506:2940: dus gsum sangs rgyas kun gyi yum //
NG0506:2942: om ta re tu re tud ta re swa ha //
NG0506:2943: ma ma swarba sid te swa ha //
NG0506:2944: om badzra b+ha ra hi na ma d+hu ma g+ha ye na ye swi d+hi hum /
NG0506:2945: om sarba b+hud d+ha da ki ni ye hum /
NG0506:2947: badzra b+he ro tsa na ye hum /
NG0506:2948: sgrol ma las kyi lha yin pas //
NG0506:2949: thun mong mchog gi las mtha' 'grub //
NG0506:2950: byin brlabs kun gyi rtsa ba ru //
NG0506:2951: bla ma'i sgrub pa mchog tu zab //
NG0506:2952: bla ma dpal ldan rdo rje 'chang *//
NG0506:2953: sangs rgyas thams cad 'dus pa'i sku //
NG0506:2954: om ma ha gu ru pad+ma thod 'phreng rtsal sid d+hi pa la hum hum hum /
NG0506:2955: om ma ni pad+me hum hri /
NG0506:2956: om pad+ma ta kri ha ya gri ba hu lu hu lu hum phat /
NG0506:2957: om da ki ni ye na ma d+ha ma g+ha ye sid+d+hi hum /
NG0506:2958: om ma ha ka la g+hu na hri ta hum /
NG0506:2959: tshe yi snying po 'di bzlas pas //
NG0506:2960: dpag tu med pa'i yon tan thob //
NG0506:2961: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje'o //
NG0506:2962: om badzra 'ag+hu ru dz+nya na swarba sid d+hi pha la hum /
NG0506:2963: om d+he ba a yu dz+nya na sarba sid+hi hum /
NG0506:2964: om d+ha ki a yu dz+nya na hum /
NG0506:2965: rnam 'joms las kyi sgrib pa sel //
NG0506:2966: bdud rtsi chu yis dri ma dri ma //
NG0506:2967: rmi lam mtshan ngan thams cad zhi /
NG0506:2968: khro bo rol pa'i dkyil 'khor mchog / rdo rje'i go 'phang thob par 'gyur //
NG0506:2969: na ma tsan d+ha badzra kro ta ye /
NG0506:2975: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i don //
NG0506:2976: gnas skabs spob pa mthar thug tu //
NG0506:2977: dbyings phyug yum gyi ngang du grol //
NG0506:2978: skye ba med pa a yi don //
NG0506:2980: b+ha ra ha ni dza la mi ti b+ha ra d+hi ni hi ri b+hi ra ta ni swaha /
NG0506:2994: wa ya ra la sha sha swaha /
NG0506:2995: om ye d+harma he du pra b+ha ba /
NG0506:2998: h+ya ba dad te shany+tsa yo ni ro d+ha ba
NG0506:2999: e bam ba di b+ha ba ma ya ma ha
NG0506:3001: mi g.yo zhes bya'i khro bo yis //
NG0506:3003: 'khor lo gsum gyis don kun byed //
NG0506:3004: ka ru na yis gdon kun 'dul //
NG0506:3005: om badzra kro d+ha tsan d+ha ma ha ro sha na hum phat /
NG0506:3006: ka ru na tsa le tsa le hum hum hum phat phat /
NG0506:3007: rdo rje'i gzhon nu'i rigs 'dzin gyis //
NG0506:3008: phur pa'i las kun grub par byed //
NG0506:3009: drag sngags rgyal po 'di nyid bzlas //
NG0506:3010: om badzra ki li ka li ki la ya sarba big+ha nan bam hum phat /
NG0506:3012: da ra ya da ra ya /
NG0506:3013: ma ra ya ma ra ya /
NG0506:3014: 'khor lo mchog gi mgon po ni //
NG0506:3015: bsdul bya gang dang gang gi don //
NG0506:3016: dus kyi 'khor lo che chung kun //
NG0506:3017: sangs rgyas rgya mtsho 'dra ba bzhugs //
NG0506:3018: bsam gyis mi khyab brjod las 'das //
NG0506:3019: 'di ni gsang chen nges pa'i lung *//
NG0506:3020: ma rig skye shi'i 'khrul pa'i yis //
NG0506:3021: srid pa bar do'i sdug bsngal las //
NG0506:3023: rnam shes bkug ste khrus byas la //
NG0506:3025: sbyong ba'i rgyal po 'di gsungs so //
NG0506:3026: na mo b+ha ga ba te sarba dur ka te /
NG0506:3028: ra tsa ya ta tha g+ha ta ya /
NG0506:3029: a ra ha te sam myag sam b+hud d+ha ya /
NG0506:3031: sho d+ha ni sho d+ha ni /
NG0506:3032: sarba pa pam b+hi sho d+ha ni shud d+he bi shud d+he /
NG0506:3038: phung po khams dang skye mched tshogs //
NG0506:3039: bde gshegs snying po'i 'gro ba rnams //
NG0506:3041: dbang du bskyed rdzogs thams cad kun //
NG0506:3042: rigs lnga lam gyi bskyed rdzogs bsgom //
NG0506:3043: sku gsung thugs yon 'phrin las kun //
NG0506:3045: bdag nyid lha bsgom ma tshigs pa //
NG0506:3046: sems dpa' bskyed pa'i dkyil 'khor dang *//
NG0506:3047: byin gyis brlabs pa 'og min nas //
NG0506:3049: lha dang gnyis med shes pa ni //
NG0506:3050: rang bzhin lhun grub dkyil 'khor yin //
NG0506:3051: phyi ni kun btags dkyil 'khor yin //
NG0506:3053: gsang ba yongs rdzogs lhun gyis grub //
NG0506:3054: mtshon byed brda yi dkyil 'khor gyis //
NG0506:3055: mtshon cha don gyi dkyil 'khor rig / rig pa rang 'byung dkyil 'khor gyis //
NG0506:3056: ye shes sku mchog dkyil 'khor mchog / rnam dag lha yi dkyil 'khor la //
NG0506:3057: phun tshogs mchod pa'i dkyil 'khor gyis //
NG0506:3058: byin rlabs dngos grub dkyil 'khor thim //
NG0506:3061: chos nyid la yang chos nyid rol //
NG0506:3063: dkyil ni chos dbyings snying po ste //
NG0506:3064: ye shes rgyal po rang yin no //
NG0506:3066: phyogs bcu'i mtha' yas mu med pas //
NG0506:3067: man+dal zhes su brjod par bya'o //
NG0506:3068: gang gis bzlas pas rgyal ba rnams //
NG0506:3069: dper na skyes chen gang zhig la //
NG0506:3070: che la myur ba'i sgras bos nas //
NG0506:3071: thos nas myur du 'ong ba bzhin //
NG0506:3072: sangs rgyas rnams ni spyan 'dren pa //
NG0506:3073: skad cig byon nas spyan gyis gzigs //
NG0506:3074: thugs rgyud bskul na byin gyis brlob //
NG0506:3075: ngag la nus pa'i yon tan gyis //
NG0506:3077: bgegs rnams ma lus bzlog pa dang *//
NG0506:3078: bdud dpung thams cad 'joms byed pa //
NG0506:3079: gsang sngags bzlas pas nus pa 'byung *//
NG0506:3080: sngags med lha yi gzugs brnyan kun //
NG0506:3082: ngag gi mngon zhen mi bzlog cing *//
NG0506:3083: nus pa'i ye shes thob mi 'gyur //
NG0506:3084: gsang sngags rgyal po don kun 'grub //
NG0506:3085: gsang sngags chen po rigs gsum mchog / phyi yi rig sngags mdo ltar bzlas //
NG0506:3086: sems can rnams kyi sgrib pa sbyangs //
NG0506:3087: nang gi gzungs sngags sngags ltar bzlas //
NG0506:3088: rang la tshogs gnyis spel bar byed //
NG0506:3089: gsang ba gsang sngags bzlas pa ni //
NG0506:3090: rdo rje gsum gyi bsnyen sgrub ste //
NG0506:3091: bskyed rim sku yi ngang nas bzlas //
NG0506:3092: bzlas pa gsung gi ngang nas bzlas //
NG0506:3093: rdzogs rim thugs kyi ngang nas bzlas //
NG0506:3094: bdud la gsang phyir gsang sngags bzlas //
NG0506:3095: dngos grub myur du thob par 'gyur //
NG0506:3096: sangs rgyas kun gyi snying po gtso //
NG0506:3097: om dang ahdang hum dang gsum //
NG0506:3098: thog mtha' bar ram gang yang rung *//
NG0506:3099: sngags rnams kun gyi srog la bzhugs //
NG0506:3100: gsang sngags snying po dang po ltar //
NG0506:3101: rang nyid lha bsgom thugs kha ru //
NG0506:3102: sa bon las ni sngags 'phreng skor /
NG0506:3104: dkar ser dmar ljang yi ge'i 'od //
NG0506:3105: mchod pa'i sprin dang bstod dbyangs su //
NG0506:3106: yar 'phros rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs //
NG0506:3107: mnyes nas dngos grub bdag la snang *//
NG0506:3108: mar 'phros sems can sgrib pa sbyangs //
NG0506:3109: thams cad lha dang lha mor 'gyur //
NG0506:3110: bar du bdag gzhan gtso 'khor rnams //
NG0506:3111: sku gsung thugs kyi yon tan ni //
NG0506:3112: snang srid bde bas gang ba yi //
NG0506:3113: gang 'dod dngos grub thob par bsam //
NG0506:3114: tshogs bsags sgrib sbyangs bzlas pa yin //
NG0506:3115: thugs kha'i sngags las sgra dang 'od //
NG0506:3116: zhal nas 'brug sgra bzhin bzlas pas //
NG0506:3118: zhi bas mi thul gdug pa can //
NG0506:3119: stong gsum dgra bgegs bdud dpung rnams //
NG0506:3120: ma rungs tshar bcad rdul du brlag / bka' sdod bran khol byed par bsam //
NG0506:3121: bar chod sel byed bzlas pa'i lugs //
NG0506:3124: gsang sngags rgyal po'i yig 'bru rnams //
NG0506:3125: phyi ru 'byung ba'i rlung gi dus //

NG0506:4024: rgyun chad med par gang snang yang *//

NG0506:4029: lus kun khyab kyang rwa 'jug nas //

NG0506:4044: rdo rje can // mtshan mo shes rab pha rol phyin //

NG0506:4052: 'od gsal chen po'i ngang la bzhugs //

NG0506:4054: chos kyi sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //

NG0506:4060: mkhas pa rnams kyi sman yin te //
NG0506:4061: brda dang don la rmongs pa yi //

NG0506:4066: kha cig dug gi rkyen gyis 'chi //

NG0506:4175: ma med pa'i snying po las //

NG0506:4270: kun dang 'bral med thugs rje de //
NG0506:4271: gdod nas lhun grub 'gyur ba med //
NG0506:4272: sangs rgyas thams cad mkhyen pa ni //
NG0506:4273: 'phrin las thogs med gcig gi don //
NG0506:4274: kun la khyab pa'i rin po che //
NG0506:4275: don gnyis phun tshogs bdag nyid do //
NG0506:4276: 'bras bu gsang ba bla na med pa'i rgyud chen po dri ma med pa'i snying po las //
NG0506:4277: 'bras bu sku dang ye shes longs spyod pa'i le'u ste bco brgyad pa'o ///
NG0506:4278: / chos nyid gcig gi gnas lugs la //
NG0506:4279: 'brel dang ma tshangs med pa dang *//
NG0506:4280: breng chags pa dang rgyun ma chad //
NG0506:4281: phun sum tshogs pa rgyud ces bya //
NG0506:4282: rgyud kyi 'brel pa rnam gsum ste //
NG0506:4283: kun gzhi chos dbyings stong pa'i rtsal //
NG0506:4284: rnam par shes pa gzhi'i rgyud //
NG0506:4285: ma rig rig pa'i ye shes su //
NG0506:4286: thabs dang shes rab zab mo yis //
NG0506:4287: gnyis med rtogs pa lam gyi rgyu //
NG0506:4288: gnas lugs 'od gsal phyag rgya che //
NG0506:4289: rang rig ye shes mngon du gyur //
NG0506:4292: gzhi dang lam dang 'bras bu gsum //
NG0506:4293: rgyud rnams kun gyi don bsdus pas //
NG0506:4294: dbyer med snying po don gyi rgyud //
NG0506:4295: thams cad ma lus kun tshang ba'i //
NG0506:4296: nam mkha' lta bu'i rgyud mchog yin //
NG0506:4297: dus gsum dus bzhi sangs rgyas kyis //
NG0506:4298: dgongs te byin gyis brlabs pa'i bka' //
NG0506:4299: rjes su gnang zhing brda bstan dang *//
NG0506:4300: zhal nas gsungs shing snyan du brgyud //
NG0506:4301: theg pa sna tshogs mtha' yas las //
NG0506:4302: brgyad khri bzhi stong grangs snyed chos //
NG0506:4303: sde snod gsum dang rgyud sde bzhi //
NG0506:4304: don kun tshangs pas spyi rgyud yin //
NG0506:4305: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa ma lus rnams //
NG0506:4306: kun gyis rtogs par bya ba'i phyir //
NG0506:4307: rgyud dang lung gi man ngag rnams //
NG0506:4308: gab dang sbas dang gsang med par //
NG0506:4309: tshig don 'khrul med gsal ba'i phyir //
NG0506:4310: dri ma med pa'i rgyud ces bya //
NG0506:4311: dam chos bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho nas //
NG0506:4312: snying po yid bzhin nor bu'i rgyud //
NG0506:4313: rdo rje sems dpa'i snying khrag 'di //
NG0506:4314: sangs rgyas bstan pa'i srog shing yin //
NG0506:4315: 'di ma rtogs pa'i sangs rgyas ni //
NG0506:4316: gcig kyang snga phyi bar gsum med //
NG0506:4317: dus gsum bde gshegs dgongs pa'i bcud //
NG0506:4318: de nyid rig byed gsang ba'i sngags //
NG0506:4319: ye shes rig pa mchog gi rgyud //
NG0506:4320: snying po gsal ba zhes bya'o //
NG0506:4321: dam chos kun gyi mthar thug pa //
NG0506:4322: gsang sngags rgyal po kun gyi bcud //
NG0506:4323: rgyud chen gsang ba'i snying po 'di //
NG0506:4324: nam mkha' mnyam pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NG0506:4325: gsang ba'i bdag po khyed kyis bsdus /
NG0506:4326: khyod kyis mkha' dang mnyam pa'i don //
NG0506:4327: skal ldan bu la gtad rgya gtod //
NG0506:4328: gang gis 'brel pa don che yang *//
NG0506:4329: ji ltar chu ni rnyog ma'i nang *//
NG0506:4330: zla ba'i gzugs brnyan mi gsal bzhin //
NG0506:4331: sangs rgyas rnams ni byon gyur kyang *//
NG0506:4332: skal ba med pas de mi rtogs //
NG0506:4334: snod ngan sbrul gdug lta bu yi //
NG0506:4335: blo dman dad brtson snying rje med //
NG0506:4336: log rtog the tshom chos brgyad can //
NG0506:4337: nga rgyal rgyud khengs mos gus chung *//
NG0506:4338: dam med rnams la rgyas btab bo //
NG0506:4339: ma 'ongs rtsod pa dar ba'i dus //
NG0506:4340: mi khoms brgyad kyi 'gro ba yang *//
NG0506:4341: nyam thag snying rje'i dus nyid du //
NG0506:4342: blo gros thabs ldan rig rtsal can //
NG0506:4343: 'gro phan snying rje ldan pa yi //
NG0506:4344: byang chub sems dpa'i rigs ldan 'byung *//
NG0506:4345: de yi dad ldan blo gros can //
NG0506:4346: shes rab bsal zhing dad brtson ldan //
NG0506:4347: thabs chen ngang tshul bzang ba'i rigs //
NG0506:4348: thar pa thob 'dod rnams la bstan //
NG0506:4350: rin chen gser gyis legs bris shing *//
NG0506:4351: sna tshogs dar gyi sbubs su gsal //
NG0506:4352: gang gis 'chang ngam mthong thos rung *//
NG0506:4353: mchod pa'i rten dang phyag byas gyur //
NG0506:4354: tshe ring nad med gdon las grol //
NG0506:4355: dpal dang bsod nams longs spyod 'phel //
NG0506:4356: rig pa sku ru smin pa yis //
NG0506:4360: gsal dag nam mkha' dngas pa 'byung *//
NG0506:4362: nyams blangs don rtogs smos ci dgos //
NG0506:4363: zab mo rgyud kyi snying po 'di //
NG0506:4364: gang na yod pa'i sa phyogs su //
NG0506:4366: skal ldan 'ga' yi spyod yul las //
NG0506:4367: kun gyis mthong thos ma yin no //
NG0506:4368: mi mjed khams kyi 'dzam bu'i gling *//
NG0506:4369: o rgyan mtshos skyes par ma 'dzin //
NG0506:4371: bde chen zhing du byang chub thob //
NG0506:4372: rgyal ba mtha' yas 'od dpag med //
NG0506:4374: byang chub sems dpar kun dang 'gro //
NG0506:4375: 'di ni gsang chen nges pa'i lung *//
NG0506:4376: gsang sngags snying po'i rgyud 'di zung *//
NG0506:4377: zhes bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa //
NG0506:4379: rang rig ye shes snying po las //
NG0506:4380: chos kyi sku ru yi rang zhing *//
NG0506:4381: 'gro don lhun grub dgyes par spyod //
NG0506:4382: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NG0506:4383: de nyid dus su dbang bskur ro //
NG0506:4384: 'di las lhag pa'i lung ma mchis //
NG0506:4385: phyogs rnams kun tu mngon par bstod //
NG0506:4386: 'bras bu gsang ba bla na med pa'i rgyud chen po dri ma med pa'i snying po las /
NG0506:4387: mtshan don gtad rgya lung gi le'u ste bcu dgu pa'o ///
NG0506:4388: / 'bras bu gsang ba bla na med pa'i rgyud
NG0506:4389: chen po dri ma med pa'i snying po zhes bya
NG0506:4390: ba'i rgyud kyi rgyal po rdzogs so ///
NG0506:4391: / o rgyan gyi mkhan po pad+ma 'byung gnas kyi zhal snga dang *//
NG0506:4392: lo tsa ba dge slong bai ro tsa nas dpal
NG0506:4393: bsam yas kyi gtsug lag khang chen por bsgyur ba'o
NG0506:4394: // phyis mnga' bdag sras on gsum gyis //
NG0506:4396: dag par gtan la phab nas //
NG0506:4398: las 'phro can dang phrad par shog cig gi smon lam btab nas //
NG0506:4399: nam mkha'i rdzong du a tham rgya /
NG0506:4401: e ma bdag 'dra pad+ma 'byung gnas kyis //
NG0506:4402: gsang sngags mthar thug rgyud mchog 'di //
NG0506:4403: rtsod ldan dus kyi lnga brgya la //
NG0506:4404: zab mo'i rgyud rnams tshig tu song *//
NG0506:4405: tha snyad mang la nyams len med //
NG0506:4406: de dus phan phyir gter du sbas //
NG0506:4407: gzhan na ma chis rgyal ba'i bka' //
NG0506:4408: las 'phro can dang phrad par shog / gter srung rnams kyis thub par srungs //
NG0506:4409: sa ma ya rgya rgya rgya /
NG0506:4410: rin chen gling pas gter nas gdan drangs shog ser la //
NG0506:4411: zhal shus bka' shog dag la bris pa'i dge ba yis //
NG0506:4412: 'di 'dzin rigs ldan rnams dang 'gro ba ma lus kun //
NG0506:4413: gsang sngags snying po'i don rtogs sangs rgyas myur thob shog / g+hu h+ye /
NG0506:4417: o rgyan thugs sras rin chen gling ba yis //
NG0506:4418: zab mo'i gter nas rgyud chen gdan drangs te //
NG0506:4419: snyigs dus 'gro ba thugs rjes nyer dgongs nas //
NG0506:4420: chos kyi bka' bkrol dar zhing rgyas @#//
NG0506:4422: gter slob kun gyis bka' drin rjed par 'phangs //
NG0506:4423: da lta'i dus na las 'phro snyom las can //
NG0506:4424: tshe 'dir thar pa'i byang chub 'dod gyur kyang *//
NG0506:4425: le lo'i dbang ngam bsod nams dman pa yis //
NG0506:4426: nyams len ma grub o rgyan thugs rjes bskul //
NG0506:4427: dge ba dri med bco lnga'i zla 'dra des //
NG0506:4428: pha mas gtso byas 'gro ba nyam thag rnams //
NG0506:4429: thar lam chen po snying po'i don rtogs nas //
NG0506:4430: bde ldan zhing du mtha' yas zhabs drung du //
NG0506:4431: dkar smug 'dab ma stong ldan ze 'bru la //
NG0506:4432: longs spyod rdzogs sku mtshan dpe ldan pa yis //
